entries.femaleVariant: In trust and secrecy lies our strength. Trust and secrecy.
And here you simply show up at Tucker's, then leave? For what? For her to patiently await your return, hm?
No. Now Tucker knows she's being hunted. No more secrecy… no more trust. Next time, realize your actions carry consequences.
